query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_trades,
  MAX(timestamp) as latest_trade,
  MIN(timestamp) as earliest_trade,
  COUNT(DISTINCT marketId) as markets_with_trades,
  SUM(CASE WHEN isWhale = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as whale_trades
FROM trades;
